title: New York zoo livestream of giraffe is pulled for nudity
text: YouTube pulls livestream of pregnant giraffe in labor after animal rights extremists complain about NUDITY and sexual content Animal Adventure Park in Harpursville, New York had placed a camera in April the giraffe's pen April had been preparing to give birth to her fourth calf on the livestream More than 20million people had tuned in to watch the giraffe before it was pulled The live video was removed from YouTube after activists complained about nudity and sexual content The stream has been back up and running since 9.45 this morning
